This paper deals with imitation learning, a subfield of machine learning that falls under the broader categories of reinforcement learning and supervised learning. The paper specifically focuses on the problem of causal confusion in behavioral cloning, which is a technique used in imitation learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
